Others: The third T20I match of Pakistan's tour to Ireland will take place on May 14, 2024, at Clontarf Cricket Club Ground in Dublin.
Live streaming of the match will be available on the Fancode app in India.
Ireland won the series opener by 5 wickets, while Pakistan won the second match by 19 runs.
Key players to watch out for include Paul Stirling (Ireland captain), Babar Azam (Pakistan captain), Fakhar Zaman, Mohammad Rizwan, and Shaheen Shah Afridi (Pakistan).
